From 0db46d4f0714f089dca54a567fd1acea7938143c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: naiyQAQ <naiy@local>
Date: Sun, 24 May 2026 14:48:04 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add libbytevc2 wrapper for ByteDance VVC decoder

---
